  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I stop my Jamster subscription from charging me money?",
  "response": "I'm sorry to hear you're having trouble with your Jamster subscription. To stop future charges, you'll need to cancel your subscription. The steps to do this depend on how you originally subscribed\u2014either through the **Apple App Store** (for iOS devices) or the **Google Play Store** (for Android devices). Here\u2019s how you can cancel your Jamster subscription on both platforms:\n\n---\n\n### **If You Subscribed via the Apple App Store (iPhone/iPad):**\n\n1. **Open Settings:**\n   - Tap on the **Settings** app on your device.\n\n2. **Access Your Apple ID:**\n   - At the top of the Settings menu, tap on your name to access your Apple ID settings.\n\n3. **Navigate to Subscriptions:**\n   - Tap on **\"Subscriptions.\"**\n\n4. **Find Jamster:**\n   - Scroll through your active subscriptions to locate the **Jamster** subscription.\n\n5. **Cancel Subscription:**\n   - Tap on **Jamster**, then select **\"Cancel Subscription.\"**\n   - Confirm the cancellation when prompted.\n\n6. **Confirmation:**\n   - You should receive a confirmation that your subscription has been canceled. Your subscription will typically remain active until the end of the current billing cycle.\n\n---\n\n### **If You Subscribed via the Google Play Store (Android):**\n\n1. **Open the Google Play Store:**\n   - Launch the **Google Play Store** app on your device.\n\n2. **Access Menu:**\n   - Tap on the **three horizontal lines** (\u2261) in the top-left corner to open the menu.\n\n3. **Go to Subscriptions:**\n   - Select **\"Subscriptions.\"**\n\n4. **Locate Jamster:**\n   - Find and tap on your **Jamster** subscription.\n\n5. **Cancel Subscription:**\n   - Tap **\"Cancel Subscription.\"**\n   - Follow the on-screen instructions to confirm cancellation.\n\n6. **Confirmation:**\n   - You should receive a confirmation email from Google Play about your canceled subscription. Your access will continue until the end of the billing period.\n\n---\n\n### **If You Subscribed Directly Through Jamster's Website:**\n\nIf you subscribed directly through Jamster's website or another platform, you'll need to cancel through their website or contact their customer support. Here's how:\n\n1. **Visit Jamster's Website:**\n   - Go to [Jamster's official website](https://www.jamster.com) (replace with the correct URL if different).\n\n2. **Log into Your Account:**\n   - Sign in using your credentials.\n\n3. **Navigate to Account Settings:**\n   - Look for a section like **\"Account,\" \"Subscriptions,\"** or **\"Billing.\"**\n\n4. **Cancel Subscription:**\n   - Find the option to **cancel your subscription** and follow the prompts.\n\n5. **Confirmation:**\n   - Ensure you receive a confirmation email or message indicating that your subscription has been canceled.\n\n---\n\n### **Additional Tips:**\n\n- **Check for Confirmation Emails:**\n  - After cancellation, keep an eye out for confirmation emails to ensure the process was successful.\n\n- **Monitor Your Bank Statements:**\n  - Verify that no further charges are applied after cancellation.\n\n- **Contact Support if Needed:**\n  - If you encounter issues while trying to cancel, consider reaching out to Jamster\u2019s customer support or the app store\u2019s support for assistance.\n\n- **App Store Subscriptions:**\n  - Remember that managing subscriptions through app stores is common, so if you can't find the subscription in one place, check the other (Apple vs. Google).\n\n---\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to successfully cancel your Jamster subscription and prevent any future charges. If you continue to experience issues, contacting Jamster's customer support directly would be the next best step.",
